	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Gradius 2 (jp) is iNES 25, which is a VRC 4 version.  With 8x 1KB chr swapping its not likely someone has put it on a USA mapper like MMC3.  
<br />
<br />As far as I know, no companies have contacted the repro makers.  You would think Nintendo would to protect their IP like Zelda (Outlands) and Mario (SMB2j).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


