<br />If you need VRC info, go here: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdevwiki.org/">http://nesdevwiki.org/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Getting the game to "run" is probably easy, but I'm guessing any IRQ or CHR banking will take a bit more effort. But I agree I think a MMC3 conversion is possible and I think that would be pretty sweet. Ofcourse I'd also love to see a Contra (J) conversion to MMC3, because the VRC2b version kicked the ass of the UNROM version.

		

